<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_06_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema522_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_06_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <span lang="y">채은이와 준희가</span>
              <div class="operation_box">
                <div class="fraction_box"><span>5</span><span>6</span></div>
                <span>×</span>
                <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>10</span></div>
              </div>
              <span lang="y">을 서로 다른 방법으로 계산했습니다.</span>
              <span class="nemo"></span><span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써 넣으세요.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box align_center">
          <div class="question_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA522_06_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
              <p lang="y" class="text1">채은</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area flex align_center gap_20 fraction_text">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>5</span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
              <span> = </span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>5 × 3</span>
                <span>6 × 10</span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span class="mark_error"
                  >15
                  <div class="input_wrap input_sep hint_up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span class="mark_error"
                  >60
                  <div class="input_wrap input_sep">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="question_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA522_06_IH/0002_02.png" alt="" />
              <p lang="y" class="text2">준희</p>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area flex align_center gap_20 fraction_text">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span class="mark_error up">5<i>1</i></span>
                <span class="mark_error"
                  >6
                  <div class="input_wrap input_sep">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span class="mark_error"
                  >3
                  <div class="input_wrap input_sep hint_up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span class="mark_error"
                  >10
                  <div class="input_wrap input_sep">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span
                  ><div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field></div
                ></span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  ×
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span
                  ><div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field></div
                ></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">채은이는 분자는 분자끼리, 분모는 분모끼리 곱한 후 약분하여 계산했고, 준희는 분자와 분모를 약분한 후 계산했습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
